headline.print_headline: Dodgers Top Angels After Teams Play Through 'Quake
headline.main: Dodgers Top Angels After Teams Play Through 'Quake

lead_paragraph: Playing through an earthquake that was felt in the ballpark, the Los Angeles Dodgers beat the Angels 5-4 in 10 innings Friday night after rookie Joc Pederson hit a tying home run in the eighth.
